00:01:48.139 --> 00:01:49.019
But

00:01:49.499 --> 00:01:51.058
I truly love Shen Jibai.

00:01:51.059 --> 00:01:52.539
That's why I got engaged to him.

00:01:54.219 --> 00:01:55.260
Regarding this matter,

00:01:55.419 --> 00:01:56.780
I've thought it over clearly.

00:01:58.779 --> 00:01:59.900
As a friend,

00:02:00.059 --> 00:02:02.579
I also hope you
find your own happiness soon.

00:02:08.619 --> 00:02:09.460
Mr. He,

00:02:10.260 --> 00:02:11.020
this way, please.

00:02:13.740 --> 00:02:14.900
We won't see you out.

00:02:29.020 --> 00:02:29.739
Boss,

00:02:29.740 --> 00:02:32.620
there's an update
on that jade pendant case.

00:02:32.939 --> 00:02:35.300
Shen Jibai probably wasn't lying.

00:02:35.659 --> 00:02:38.500
But I discovered
that his mother, Shen Yi,

00:02:38.580 --> 00:02:41.620
seems to have some connection
to your grandfather's family, the Ye's.

00:02:47.339 --> 00:02:48.340
Who is it?

00:02:48.539 --> 00:02:49.539
It's me.

00:03:04.659 --> 00:03:05.379
See?

00:03:06.219 --> 00:03:07.939
I told you Zhiyu wasn't asleep yet.

00:03:08.260 --> 00:03:09.139
Zhiyu,

00:03:09.339 --> 00:03:12.019
