00:03:12.020 --> 00:03:13.500
and you're getting married soon.

00:03:14.180 --> 00:03:15.299
If you ask me,

00:03:15.300 --> 00:03:16.938
you two should just live together.

00:03:16.939 --> 00:03:18.099
You're young people,

00:03:18.260 --> 00:03:19.659
so it's normal to be open-minded.

00:03:19.900 --> 00:03:20.859
Right?

00:03:22.099 --> 00:03:23.379
You're right.

00:03:25.300 --> 00:03:27.020
It's getting late.

00:03:27.339 --> 00:03:29.340
Jibai and I are going to rest.

00:03:29.939 --> 00:03:31.179
You should get some sleep too.

00:03:31.180 --> 00:03:31.939
Okay.

00:03:38.787 --> 00:03:40.761
(Young people
are like dry wood and fire.)

00:03:40.762 --> 00:03:42.723
