00:04:51.419 --> 00:04:53.140
I'll get you a glass of ice water.

00:04:55.219 --> 00:04:56.499
Don't go.

00:04:59.219 --> 00:05:00.499
You're so hot too.

00:05:04.437 --> 00:05:05.677
I'm not leaving.

00:05:07.060 --> 00:05:08.539
I'm just getting you some water.

00:05:11.779 --> 00:05:13.136
Your body is burning up.

